data.description: Charming Woodbury quad townhome with great potential. This home features two bedrooms on the main floor with an owner’s suite walk through and walk-in closet. The home has been freshly painted and is ready for your finishing touches. There’s new plank flooring installed in the lower level family room that has room to create an office or additional bedroom.  HOA says FHA is ok. The city of Woodbury has new ordinances regarding rental properties coming out in 2024, Buyer to confirm and verify any information.
